text: Tongguan railway station () is a railway station of Longhai railway located in Tongguan County, Weinan, Shaanxi, China. The station is the easternmost station operated by CR Xi'an on Longhai railway. == History == The station was opened in 1931. == References == Category:Railway stations in Shaanxi Category:Stations on the Longhai Railway Category:Railway stations in China opened in 1931
title: Tongguan railway station
